WEBVTT

00:01.383 --> 00:04.018
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.086 --> 00:05.670
Hey, everybody.

00:07.073 --> 00:08.306
So, what's the latest?

00:08.374 --> 00:10.158
Frasier passed out about 3:00.

00:10.225 --> 00:11.543
Aw! Poor guy.

00:11.544 --> 00:13.411
Yeah. For someone whose
wife is leaving him,

00:13.412 --> 00:17.048
he seems awfully upset.

00:17.116 --> 00:20.385
Oh, God! My head! Sam,

00:20.453 --> 00:22.087
uh... coffee, please.

00:22.154 --> 00:26.491
Oh, Carla, uh...
about last night...

00:26.559 --> 00:28.427
I was in pretty bad shape,
you know?

00:28.428 --> 00:30.828
I was drunk, and I was
carrying on about Lilith.

00:30.829 --> 00:34.532
And I have this
half-memory of you

00:34.600 --> 00:38.270
dragging me
into the office and cleaning me up,

00:38.337 --> 00:39.837
putting me on the couch,

00:39.905 --> 00:42.240
laying a blanket
over me and-and...

00:42.308 --> 00:44.476
and sitting with me
until I fell asleep.

00:44.543 --> 00:46.678
And, well, even
in my drunken stupor,

00:46.746 --> 00:50.148
I wanted to thank you for
your... your unexpected kindness. Thanks.

00:50.215 --> 00:51.983
Glad to help.

00:52.050 --> 00:53.267
Here's your coffee.

00:53.335 --> 00:55.403
Thank you, Sam.

00:55.471 --> 00:57.171
Geez!
What time is it?

00:57.239 --> 00:58.673
You know,

00:58.741 --> 01:00.959
I could have sworn
I had my Rolex on.

01:01.026 --> 01:05.080
FRASIER:
Hey, where's my class ring?

01:08.567 --> 01:12.354
(theme song begins)

01:12.356 --> 01:14.222
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:14.290 --> 01:19.760
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:19.828 --> 01:24.182
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:24.250 --> 01:26.651
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:26.718 --> 01:29.370
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:29.438 --> 01:34.175
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

